<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<%= stylesheet_link_tag "style"%>
		<title> Dice Game Rules </title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Welcome to the Dice Game</h1>

		<p>Here are the rules:</p>

		<ul>
			<li> Roll the dice to start the game</li>
			<li> If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win.</li>
			<li> If your first roll is a 2, 3, or 12, you lose.</li>
			<li> Anything else becomes your <em>goal</em>. Roll your goal again before 
				a 7 and you win. Roll a 7 before your goal and you lose.</li>
		</ul>

		<p><a href="roll/?goal=0">Roll Dice</a> </p>
	</body>
</html>
